# Small-terminal check (~80x24)
Output polish_shots/small-throwaway.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 700
Set Height 400
Set Padding 8

Type "./target/release/govee-tui"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Screenshot polish_shots/small_list.png

Type "j"
Sleep 300ms
Type "j"
Sleep 300ms
Type "j"
Sleep 300ms
Type "j"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
Screenshot polish_shots/small_detail.png

Type "?"
Sleep 2s
Screenshot polish_shots/small_help.png
Escape
Sleep 500ms
Type "q"
Sleep 1s
